==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hoodlum
<hw>Hood"lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A young rowdy; a
rough, lawless fellow; colloquially, called also
<altname>hood</altname>.</def> <mark>[Colloq. U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Just tell your <ex>hoodlum</ex> friends outside⟦br⟧
You ain't got time to take no ride.</q> <rj><au>Yakety-Yak
(Song)</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hoodman</ent>⟦br⟧
